06:46.707 --> 06:49.643
I come here to see my daughter.

06:51.745 --> 06:53.514
Word.

06:53.547 --> 06:55.382
That's why I'm here.

06:55.415 --> 06:57.151
To see my family.

06:57.184 --> 07:00.054
They may not know it,
they may not want it,

07:00.087 --> 07:02.623
but you're coming here
to visit them

07:02.656 --> 07:05.125
is the most important thing
you can do

07:05.158 --> 07:07.427
to somebody that's locked up
in a place like this.

07:11.264 --> 07:13.734
I don't know
why I'm here, man.

07:13.767 --> 07:16.369
I haven't been happy with her.

07:18.238 --> 07:21.075
Just feels like
I needed to do something.

07:21.108 --> 07:24.078
- So I'm doing it.
- Well, that's a risk.

07:24.111 --> 07:27.080
But you're listening
to your heart, that's good.

07:29.316 --> 07:31.385
Are you a guru?

07:31.418 --> 07:33.320
Or a philosopher or something?

07:33.353 --> 07:35.589
Nah, I'm not a philosopher.

07:35.622 --> 07:38.325
I'm just an old hippie dude
that's done a lot of acid.

07:38.358 --> 07:40.227
It makes you think.

07:40.260 --> 07:43.297
When you're my age,
there's a lot to think about.

07:43.330 --> 07:45.099
I live by a few rules.

07:45.132 --> 07:47.601
Be kind to those
that you're closest to.

07:47.634 --> 07:51.272
Wear a good hat
and a good pair of boots.

07:51.305 --> 07:53.207
A good hat helps hide
what you're doing

07:53.240 --> 07:55.576
from the Lord above,
and good boots,

07:55.609 --> 07:58.245
they help you outrun the Devil.

07:58.278 --> 07:59.680
