for a second.

18:31.411 --> 18:35.282
Remember the stories I told you
when you were growing up,

18:35.315 --> 18:38.084
about the people we come from.

18:40.854 --> 18:43.223
Generations of medicine people.

18:45.659 --> 18:48.094
Caretakers.

18:50.564 --> 18:53.434
These are the ones...

18:53.467 --> 18:56.804
