we arrived from our homelands.

19:01.541 --> 19:07.080
The healers who carried us
and buried us as we marched.

19:08.315 --> 19:12.352
Men and women whose songs
led us through the dark.

19:13.387 --> 19:16.523
They're watching you, my girl.

19:19.526 --> 19:23.096
You don't need me.
You have them.

19:29.369 --> 19:32.706
This is the power we carry.

19:35.242 --> 19:40.347
When you really pray,
they're all around you.

19:40.380 --> 19:43.049
All the time.

19:44.718 --> 19:48.255
Oh, shit.

19:54.261 --> 19:57.231
Takes focus, though.

19:57.264 --> 19:59.233
Intent.

20:06.506 --> 20:08.676
Open your eyes.

20:12.646 --> 20:16.116
- Holy fuck.

20:23.390 --> 20:25.826
Oh, shit.

20:25.859 --> 20:27.627
Ah, fuck.

20:37.371 --> 20:41.074
I spent a lot of energy
trying to fix Danny.

20:43.510 --> 20:45.346
Instead, I took on his pain.

20:45.379 --> 20:48.048
We shared it.

20:49.149 --> 20:52.519
Can't love someone out of
hurting themselves, though.

20:54.288 --> 20:56.490
I was so focused on Danny,

20:56.523 --> 21:00.527
so focused on myself that...

21:00.560 --> 21:02.062
:
I couldn't see...

21:07.534 --> 21:10.036
You can't help people
who don't want to be helped.

21:11.238 --> 21:15.075
- I learned that the hard way.

21:15.108 --> 21:18.212
You create the space
for your friends.

21:18.245 --> 21:20.780
You do it with intention.

21:23.150 --> 21:26.353
Either the path will be
laid for you, or won't.

21:26.386 --> 21:30.224
I know they want to be helped,

21:30.257 --> 21:33.494
but I don't know
how to bring them together.

21:33.527 --> 21:35.629
Christ, girl.

21:35.662 --> 21:38.064
Weren't you paying attention?

21:40.133 --> 21:41.602
