right in front of you.

21:44.171 --> 21:46.073
Hey.

21:46.106 --> 21:48.108
Come here.

21:56.650 --> 21:58.084
Okay, that's enough.

22:02.255 --> 22:03.390
I'm ready.

22:03.423 --> 22:05.759
You take that letter with you.

22:07.427 --> 22:09.563
