Sup, Bear?

23:31.478 --> 23:33.046
What's up, Elora?

23:44.224 --> 23:46.059
Why are we here?

24:16.623 --> 24:19.059
Well, this has been fun.

24:25.632 --> 24:28.034
I went and saw Hokti.

24:29.069 --> 24:30.303
Whoa.

24:31.271 --> 24:32.472
In jail?

24:34.341 --> 24:36.343
Yep.

24:37.511 --> 24:39.346
How is she?

24:39.379 --> 24:41.649
She's good.

24:41.682 --> 24:43.583
Looks all healthy and shit.

24:45.218 --> 24:46.686
Smoking paper cigs.

24:51.525 --> 24:54.361
