24:54.394 --> 24:58.198
I needed some advice about...

24:58.231 --> 25:00.033
all of us.

25:01.602 --> 25:03.737
What about us?

25:03.770 --> 25:05.306
You know what I'm talking about, bro.

25:05.339 --> 25:07.074
This is weird.

25:07.107 --> 25:10.177
