or see each other anymore.

25:10.210 --> 25:12.613
Man, everything is fine.

25:12.646 --> 25:16.250
Yeah. Everything's totally fine.

25:16.283 --> 25:17.484
Yeah.

25:20.554 --> 25:22.422
Wow, that was convincing.

25:27.394 --> 25:29.429
